                                    <i class="fa fa-rocket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="cd-doc-card-title">Getting Started</h3>
                                <p class="cd-doc-card-desc">Download, install, and set up your Consumer Wallet. Complete your first login and explore the app interface.</p>
                                <div class="cd-doc-card-arrow">Learn more <i class="fa fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                </div>
